title: Disclosure’s Edge: UFO Doc Ignites Clash Between Insiders and Scientists
description: A new UFO documentary featuring James Clapper and 34 officials alleges an 80-year non-human tech cover-up, sparking Capitol Hill buzz and Trump disclosure speculation. Scientists at Virginia Tech demand evidence, pointing to K2-18b biosignatures as superior leads.

title: Third-ever interstellar comet spotted as NASA debunks rumors of alien craft
description: NASA Associate Administrator Amit Kshatriya said that despite many rumors about the traveler, it was definitely a comet, not a spacecraft from another star as some have claimed.
